# Lab2 – LEDs, Buttons, Interrupts

**Discipline:** Programming Technologies C / Embedded  
**Student:** Совенко Микита  
**Group:** ФІОТ, 3 курс  
**Platform:** Arduino UNO (Tinkercad)

## Description
Program controls 4 LEDs connected to digital pins D2–D5.
Four different blinking algorithms are implemented.
Modes are switched automatically every 3 seconds (remote mode).

## Pin configuration
- D2 – LED 1
- D3 – LED 2
- D4 – LED 3
- D5 – LED 4
- GND – common ground

## Implemented modes
1. Running light
2. All LEDs blinking
3. Pair blinking
4. Checkerboard blinking

